HEADWORD: Proletary
<hw>Prol"e*ta*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Proletaries</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[ L.
<ets>proletarius</ets>, fr. <ets>proles</ets> offspring. Cf.
<er>Prol⟦eacute⟧taire</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Rom. Antiq.)</fld> <def>A
